Do you use editing on the multi effect board?Editing is defined as adjusting a parameter of an effect i.e. increasing the delay.

Which mode do you use your multi effect board in?The major difference between multi effect board is their modes that they can be used in.Presets: Combination of different effects, when pressed all the effect to the specific preset is activated.Effects: Manually gives an effect when playing (ie. given it more distortion) by pressing a button with your feet.Set lists: If you play a song with different presets or effects within the song that you want to go through, but only want to push one button. You can then set presets in series of each other and only press on the same button when you want the next preset/effect to occur.
